casebody.data:
ELLIOTT v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 11,

September Term, 1961 (Adv.).]

Decided June 23, 1961.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, Horney and Marbury, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons stated by Judge Allen for dismissing the petition, the application for leave to appeal is denied.

Application denied.
